_:N53642383913e47f1a9a47bff7cb10f93 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Jake Richards was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Justice and as Assistant Whip, House of Commons on 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Rother Valley in July 2024.</p>\n" .
